00:07:42.070 --> 00:07:50.400
And we get 10x over 13 minus
x is equal to minus 15.

00:07:50.400 --> 00:07:52.040
Let me scroll down
a little bit.

00:07:52.040 --> 00:07:53.300
And so, what is this?

00:07:53.300 --> 00:08:01.430
This is the same thing as 10x
over 13 minus 13x over 13.

00:08:01.430 --> 00:08:02.570
That's just x.

