Is equal to minus 14.

00:08:04.470 --> 00:08:10.310
And then, 10 minus 13, this is
equal to -- so this is minus 3x

00:08:10.310 --> 00:08:17.180
over 13, is equal to minus 15.

00:08:17.180 --> 00:08:20.420
Now, we can just multiply
both sides of this equation

00:08:20.420 --> 00:08:24.570
by minus 13 over 3.

00:08:24.570 --> 00:08:28.460
Multiply this side
by minus 13 over 3.

00:08:28.460 --> 00:08:31.300
I picked that number so that
this and that cancel out.

00:08:31.300 --> 00:08:34.080
And that and that cancel out,
and the negatives cancel out.

00:08:34.080 --> 00:08:36.740
So I'm just left with
x on that side.

00:08:36.740 --> 00:08:39.080
And then, the right-hand
side becomes what?

00:08:39.080 --> 00:08:41.010
The negatives cancel out.

00:08:41.010 --> 00:08:45.260
I can divide the 15 and the 3
by 3, so that becomes a 5.

00:08:45.260 --> 00:08:47.260
And then this becomes a 1.

00:08:47.260 --> 00:08:49.510
And I'm just left
with 5 times 13.

00:08:49.510 --> 00:08:52.380
This was just, times plus 13, I
wrote that just to make sure

00:08:52.380 --> 00:08:54.740
that you understood that the
negatives canceled out.

00:08:54.740 --> 00:08:56.390
So, 5 times 13 is what?

00:08:56.390 --> 00:09:00.320
5 times 12 is 60, so
